    接口 说明

    Callback to notify the Lifecycle of car service.

    Listener to get notification for app getting information on app type ownership loss.

    Listener to monitor any Occupant Zone configuration change.

    Interface to receive for projection status updates.
    CarRemoteDeviceManager.StateCallback
    A callback to allow the client to monitor other occupant zones in the car and peer clients in those occupant zones.
    ResultCallback<V>
    Callback for generic results.
